{"id":"8011","name":"bright-early-were-baaaack-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: We&#x2019;re Baaaack Edition","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2012-01-03T10:30:00-06:00","tags":[],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/fallingwater123/6620370663/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7022/6620370663_b99940a990.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville, and happy 2012! We&#x2019;ve enjoyed our extended holiday break but we&#x2019;re ready to get back to the daily grind. In case you haven&#x2019;t noticed, <a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2012/01/bitter-chill-today-slick-spots-near-plateau/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">it&#x2019;s cold today</a>. Those balmy December days in the mid-60&#x2032;s have given way to temperatures in the 30&#x2032;s, overnight flurries and a <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/story/16428437/cumberland-plateau-snow\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">handful of school closings</a> along the Cumberland Plateau. But hang in there, because it&#x2019;ll be back in the 50&#x2032;s and maybe even 60&#x2032;s by the end of the week. In unrelated news, <a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2012/01/wave-clouds/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">look at these cool wave clouds that showed up in Birmingham last month</a>! Can we get some of those?</p><ul><li><strong>Good game</strong>. <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/16431956/season-over-for-titans-players-clean-out-lockers\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The season is over for the Titans</a>, who wrapped things up on Sunday with a final victory over the Houston Texans, bringing their season record to nine and seven.</li><li><strong>Music note mishap</strong>. Is it still the new year if the ball (or in this case, music note) doesn&#x2019;t drop at midnight? Let&#x2019;s hope so, because <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/16429941/music-note-fails-to-fall-at-midnight\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville&#x2019;s music note got stuck this year</a> as the clock struck twelve on January 1.</li><li><strong>Hang on a minute</strong>. The Williamson County sheriff&#x2019;s office has been slapped with a federal lawsuit claiming that the office <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20120103/WILLIAMSON/301030015/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">wrongfully detained immigrants</a> without the permission of US Immigration and Customs Enforcement.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces</strong>. <a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/nashville/morning_call/2011/12/drunken-online-buying-may-be-growing.html?ana=RSS&amp;s=article_search&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+bizj_nashville+%28Nashville+Business+Journal%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.bizjournals.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Drunk online shopping is the latest trend</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/story/16433347/murfreesboro-protests-ends-with-cold-weather\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Occupy Murfreesboro has packed up</a> their encampment &#x2026; The annual January 1 Percy Priest&#xA0;<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/16428563/dozens-participate-in-annual-polar-bear-plunge\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Polar Bear Plunge was well attended</a> as always &#x2026; A <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/16426087/nashville-psychic-weighs-in-on-2012\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville psychic assures us that the world will not end in 2012</a> (oh, and that T. Swift will win Entertainer of the Year again)&#xA0;&#x2026; The <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/16434720/yearlong-roundabout-project-begins-in-nashville\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">yearlong roundabout construction project at 8th &amp; Lafayette has begun</a>, so basically, avoid 8th Avenue until 2013 &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/16434696/carole-king-performs-benefit-at-bluebird-cafe\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Carole King performed at the Bluebird last night</a> &#x2026; The city of <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/16429479/hackers-steal-175k-from-city-of-portland\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Portland, TN is out $175k after hackers drained the city&#x2019;s water and sewer bank account</a> &#x2026; Civil rights attorneys may be preparing to file <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20120103/NEWS0201/301030024/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">challenges to Tennessee&#x2019;s new voter ID law</a>.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/fallingwater123/6620370663/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">fallingwater123</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/01/04/bright-early-waking-up-in-the-tundra-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Waking Up In The Tundra Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Waking Up In The Tundra Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/02/22/bright-early-call-to-arms-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Call To Arms Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Call To Arms Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}